sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant Svc as Service
    participant Redis as Redis
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over C,G: First request (Cache Miss)

    C->>G: GET /api/zones
    G->>Svc: Forward request
    
    Svc->>Redis: GET cache:zones:all
    Redis-->>Svc: null (miss)
    
    Svc->>DB: SELECT * FROM zones
    DB-->>Svc: zones data (50 rows)
    
    Svc->>Svc: Process data
    
    Svc->>Redis: SET cache:zones:all<br/>VALUE: JSON<br/>EX: 1800 (30min)
    Redis-->>Svc: OK
    
    Svc-->>G: Response + data
    G-->>C: 200 OK

    Note over C,G: Second request (Cache Hit)

    C->>G: GET /api/zones
    G->>Svc: Forward request
    
    Svc->>Redis: GET cache:zones:all
    Redis-->>Svc: cached data
    
    Svc-->>G: Response (no DB call!)
    G-->>C: 200 OK (X-Cache-Status: HIT)

    Note over C,G: Cache Invalidation

    Svc->>G: POST /api/zones<br/>{new zone}
    G->>Svc: Forward
    
    Svc->>DB: INSERT new zone
    DB-->>Svc: OK
    
    Svc->>Redis: DEL cache:zones:all
    Svc->>Redis: DEL cache:stats:*
    Svc->>Redis: DEL cache:containers:*
    
    Redis-->>Svc: OK
    
    Svc-->>G: 201 Created
    G-->>C: 201 Created (cache cleared)
    %% Cache Strategy
    %% Endpoint | TTL | Strategy
    %% /zones | 30 min | Cache-first
    %% /containers | 5 min | Cache-first
    %% /stats | 2 min | Cache-first
    %% /measurements | 1 min | Cache-first
    %% /tournees/active | 30 sec | No cache
    %% /users/* | No cache | -